title: Adalat
subTitle: Dharma leaves his village and moves to Mumbai to lead a better life. However, things take an ugly turn when the police suspects his connection in a criminal case and arrests him.

title: Anamika
subTitle: A writer rescues an injured woman who suffers from memory loss but claims to be his wife. In the process of finding out her real identity, he falls in love with her.

title: Amir Garib
subTitle: Mohanlal, a musician and a thief, robs rich people and distributes the money amongst the poor. However, things take a turn when he falls for Sunita, a wealthy man's daughter.

title: Videsh
subTitle: A drug lord escapes from India to Britain, assuming the identity of Swami Prem Babu to continue his illegal activities. When he learns that CBI Inspector Prasad Sinha is investigating him, he kidnaps Sinha's daughter.

title: Khoon Ki Pukaar
subTitle: A compassionate pujari, Vidya, shelters a maimed bandit, unaware of his hidden motives. Subsequently, Vidya must confront a moral dilemma that could change their lives forever.

title: Jheel Ke Us Paar
subTitle: Sameer falls in love with Neelu, a girl with visual impairment, and plans to restore her sight. However, his mother disapproves of their union and hatches a plot to break them apart.

title: Ganga Jamuna
subTitle: Ganga and Jumna, two orphaned brothers, grow up to find themselves on opposite sides of the law when one becomes a police officer and the other turns into a dreaded gangster.

title: Jawab Hum Denge
subTitle: Accused of murder, Vijay Saxena, a union leader, confronts not only his employer, Dhanraj, but also the justice system, seeking to clear his name while continuing his fight for workers' rights.

title: Andaz
subTitle: Sheetal, a widow, is a school teacher and lives with her son after her husband's death. She meets her student's father Ravi, a widower, and decides to marry him.

title: Dost
subTitle: Maanav befriends Gopichand, a reformed thief, and helps him secure a job to turn his life around. However, Maanav suddenly disappears and returns just in time to support Gopichand during a crisis.

title: Dost

title: Yeh to Kamaal Ho Gaya
subTitle: A corrupt lawyer implicates a burglar's son in a false case of murder. Eventually, the burglar kidnaps the lawyer's son and trains him in the art of crime and burglary to exact his revenge.

title: Kab Tak Chup Rahungi
subTitle: On her trip to a remote and scenic village, Geeta meets Gopal, a local guide. The two fall in love but she is forcefully married to a rich industrialist who does not respect her.

title: Nai Imarat
subTitle: Movie starring Parikshit Sahni, Vidya Sinha and directed by Ram Pahlwa, Sharad Batra.

title: Aashiq Hoon Baharon Ka
subTitle: Chaos ensues as Vikram, driven by greed and ego, hinders the blossoming romance between Ashok and Veera by trapping Ashok with false accusations of theft.

title: The Train
subTitle: An honest CBI officer must investigate a series of murders on a train. However, as he makes progress in the case, he finds disturbing leads.

title: Mehboob Ki Mehndi
subTitle: Shabana is employed by Yusuf, a rich man, to teach his nephew. Eventually, Yusuf and Shabana fall in love and plan to get married. But the girl has a troubled past that may destroy her future.

title: Kudrat
subTitle: When Chandramukhi visits Shimla, she realises that she was Paro, a girl who is raped and murdered, in her previous life. Thereafter, she decides to punish her culprits and get justice.

title: Mehbooba
subTitle: Suraj, a singer, takes refuge from a storm in a rest house. During his stay, he has a strange feeling that he has been there before and recalls memories of being with a woman called Ratna.

title: Prem Kahani
subTitle: Rajesh, an apolitical poet, is in love with Kamini and leads a peaceful life. However, when his brother is killed by the British government, he decides to become a revolutionary and joins the freedom struggle.

title: Prem Kahani

title: Sadhu Aur Shaitaan
subTitle: Sher Khan, a criminal, decides to rob a bank. However, his life takes a dramatic turn when he meets a kind-hearted taxi driver.

title: Story Of Gauri Putra Ganesh
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Tere Mere Beech Mein
subTitle: A carefree country bumpkin's simple life turns chaotic and comical when he unexpectedly inherits a fortune, leading to hilarious misadventures as he navigates wealth and its unexpected challenges.

title: Singhasan
subTitle: When the kingdoms Avanti and Gandharva are attacked by the enemies, the commander in chief of the latter decides to outwit everyone else.

title: Baseraa
subTitle: Nima and Balraj's life is thrown out of gear when her sister and Balraj's first wife, Sharada, returns home after spending 14 years in a mental asylum.

title: Beta Ho To Aisa
subTitle: When Laxmi's servant is killed, she brings up his son Raju with her own children. When they get involved in some shady dealings, it's up to Raju to sort out the mess his family is in.

title: Khatron Ke Khiladi
subTitle: Balwant, a truck driver, is driven into the underworld as he wants to take revenge on the owners of the trucking company for the death of his brother.

title: Dil Ne Phir Yaad Kiya
subTitle: Ashok, a salesman, is in love with Ashoo and wants to marry her. However, things take a turn when his brother kidnaps Ashoo.
